# exam-papers

Go CLI/API for fetching Irish State Exam papers from examinations.ie.

1. Build: `go build -o exam-papers ./cmd/exam-papers/`
2. Unit tests: `go test ./pkg/examapi/ -run 'Test[^I]'`
3. Integration tests: `EXAM_INTEGRATION=1 go test ./pkg/examapi/ -run TestIntegration`
4. The site obfuscates URLs with shifted ASCII codes (random offset per page load). Parse action values from each HTML response.
5. Rate limiting via Cloudflare. Client uses delays + exponential backoff on 403/429.
6. Direct PDF access: `https://www.examinations.ie/archive/{type}/{year}/{fileID}`
7. Subject codes: 1=Irish, 2=English, 3=Maths, 21=Physics, 22=Chemistry, 25=Biology
